====Standard Setup====
*{{RedGunMedium}}Main Gun x2 + {{Radar}}Radar OR Wildcard + {{Seaplane}}Recon Seaplane
* Standard setup for heavy cruisers which allows day and night double attack.
* The wildcard can be anything as long as its not a {{RedGunMedium}}, {{GreenGunDP}}, {{YellowGun}} or {{TorpedoWeapon}}.
* Requires getting [[Aerial Combat|air superiority]].
** In case installations are involved, you can substitute the wildcard for a {{GreenAmmo}}[[Type 3 Shell]].
** In case you're using either {{ShipLink|Zara Kai}} or {{ShipLink|Pola Kai}}, you can substitute the wildcard with a <br />{{Seaplane Fighter}}[[Seaplane Fighters]] if you wish.
*** You are not recommended to use {{Seaplane}}[http://kancolle.wikia.com/wiki/Seaplane#Seaplane_Bombers Seaplane Bombers], because of their very small slot sizes. Using {{Seaplane Fighter}}[[Seaplane Fighters]] however, is fine.


====Night Double Attack (No AS)====
*{{RedGunMedium}}Main Gun + {{YellowGun}} '''OR''' {{GreenGunDP}}Secondary Gun x3
* Mainly used when [[Artillery Spotting]] is not possible.
* Maximizes firepower while maintaining double attack.
* {{Firepower}} is what matters in the end with this setup, simply use your strongest guns to build this setup with your CA.
* This setup is not recommended if you only have access to [[15.2cm Single Gun Mount]], because of the terrible stats. You are better off using the standard setup instead.


====Night Cut In====
*{{TorpedoWeapon}}[[Torpedo]] x2 + '''Wildcard''' x2; {{TorpedoWeapon}}[[Torpedo]] x4
* Setup focused on dealing heavy damage (150%*2) through a Torpedo Cut In during night battle.
* This setup is generally reserved for high {{Luck}} ships.
* Torpedo cut-in is only marginally stronger than the double attack, but activates less often and is inconsistent. Use this only if it is truly necessary.


====Maya AACI====
*{{GreenGunMG}}[http://kancolle.wikia.com/wiki/List_of_Anti-Air_Guns_by_stats Concentrated Deployment] + {{GreenGunDP}} + {{Radar}}[http://kancolle.wikia.com/wiki/List_of_Radars_by_stats Air Radar] + {{RedGunMedium}} '''OR''' {{GreenGunDP}}
* A special setup for {{ShipLink|Maya Kai Ni}} which allows her to use the best AACI in the game while retaining the ability to double attack during night. Note that this specific setup only works for {{ShipLink|Maya Kai Ni}}.
* Guns qualified for Concentrated Deployment are {{GreenGunMG}}[[25mm Triple Autocannon Mount (Concentrated Deployment)|25mm CD]], {{GreenGunMG}}[[Bofors 40mm Quadruple Autocannon Mount|Bofors]] and {{GreenGunMG}}[[QF 2-pounder Octuple Pom-pom Gun Mount|Pom-pom]] guns.



